text: Mikyashevo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Mikyashevsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 782 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 32 km from Davlekanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Mikyashevo
